      <scopecontent id="aspace_f345831408a3afbdcb09cf14c34c4950">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains examples of drawings and paintings on paper. Many of these pieces were intended for use or used as illustrations in published works. The majority of the collection is late 19th century. There are two paintings on unstretched canvas.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a59c0b857a34da6185ec5de14d55bc27">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into six series: I. Figurative. II. Landscape/Architecture. III. Maps. IV. Nature. V. Ornamentation. VI. Miscellaneous.</p>  
      </arrangement>
